      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SANDAVE ABLAZE (2) goes very well here starting 29 times for 11 wins and eight minors. In the money last time at this track (25.32) in a NG, finishing a nose second. Expected to be in the finish. CASH CRUISE (8) missed the frame and was safely held latest finishing 8th at Q Parklands following on from a second place finish (29.85) there the start prior. Has a strong record out of this box with two wins and a minor placing from three starts. Can figure in the finish. LADY JACQUELINE (1) ran below best last time finishing seventh (26.82) over 450m at this track from Box 1. The form from her last run is stacking up nicely. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. LOCAL LEGEND (3) is a last-start placegetter in a fast-run race - should be thereabouts.",
